{"tid":482182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，QR真係完勝八達通，不服來辯","createTime":"2017-11-28T02:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T23:51:54.000Z","uid":1303,"like":133,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bb345d3ee340600a5dfaec89ffea6f4bd2f76043","tid":482182,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚on9啦，發夢你就完勝呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無可否認大陸用QR係用到一地都係，但唔撚係因為QR呢樣野本身有咩優勢囉<br />\n人地係各個層面都應用得普及先係個核心，唔係話個技術有咩咁優勝。<br />\n八達通有幾樣野可以做 :<br />\n1. 加大個limit。$1000一定唔夠做，人地國家名店都可以用QR比。<br />\n2. 要更普及係日常生活入面。最簡單人地國家搭部的士都可以QR比，我地班低賤DC9仲係要比現金。<br />\n3. 推廣自動增值。人地國家d QR唔駛成日排隊係7仔增值。<br />\n<br />\n做到上面3樣，八達通起碼再屌打人地國家10年啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不服來辯</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724e3e202a687ea06b2ed0bdb9fdb60342ad9ec8","tid":482182,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj